Years ago back in high school some uncool loner dweeb suggested I play something called League of Legends because I would really like it. Yeah right, leave me alone you piece of disintegrated sandpaper. Six months later holidays come around and I start playing with everyone else. Saw that same loner dweeb all alone at an expo years later lol.

Wait, that&#039;s my life now, FUCK. {{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} 


What&#039;s yours? Am bored, go.
